<p>I illustrated the book around 2020 but the book just got published in mid-2022. It was one of the very first illustration projects that I did for a bigger publisher and I learned a lot in the process that took almost a year to draw 200 pages of it.
I‚Äôm so grateful to have been through this and to have the book finished.</p>

